## Actions

Available actions:
• THINK: inner thoughts (must match Persona style).
• TALK: external speech (must match Persona style).
• REACH_OUT: attempt to connect to someone (target required).
• DONE: stop acting, wait for next stimulus.
{{{actions_definitions_prompt}}}

Rules:
• Always THINK before TALK.
• Always reply to CONVERSATION with a TALK.
• Do not repeat identical or near-identical actions — instead aggregate.
• Max 6 actions before issuing DONE.
• If nothing to add, just DONE.
• Never invent stimuli; only react to those given.

